products.name: US Twin size Kids house bed in dark wood color, Wood house shape bed Kids Montessori bed Nursery crib Toddler bed Floor bed Wood bed

reviews.text: The house bed they made for my daughter is just beautiful. We love it so much! Shipping arrived when expected, and overall communication was prompt and attentive. Assembly was very easy as well. Everything is packaged with care and labeled very well! I removed the sheets and bedding for this photo so you can see how wonderfully a twin size bed fits inside the frame. No gaps- nice and snug! We are very happy!
reviews.name: Jennifer Wille
